    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a brand-new car. It has been meticulously cared for, stored in a climate-controlled garage, and features a flawless exterior finish with no scratches or dents. The interior is pristine, still retaining its new-car scent, with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and very low mileage. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. This is a rare opportunity for a buyer seeking a showroom-quality example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
