    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, showroom-quality condition, representing the absolute pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster with no scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and the body panels are perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows no wear or creasing, and all original electronic features, from the navigation system to the heated seats, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, with a smooth, powerful engine and a transmission that shifts with precision. It has been exclusively garage-kept and comes with a complete, documented service history from the local dealership. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the showroom floor, requiring no immediate maintenance or cosmetic attention.",
      "price": 48900.0,
