    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it is in absolutely pristine condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. You seriously won't find a scratch on it! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner so happy. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
