      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering. This specimen features a perfectly maintained 13B-REW rotary engine with its sequential twin-turbocharger system providing seamless boost transition and optimal compression. The chassis dynamics are preserved by original aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring clinical precision through the corners. Every vacuum line, bushing, and seal is in factory-fresh state, with zero oxidation on the undercarriage. This unmolested example boasts original high-gloss finish and a pristine interior, representing the zenith of JDM performance preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
