    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the most discerning collector. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or imperfection. Every panel alignment is factory-perfect, reflecting its history of being exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of wear or creasing, while the dashboard and trim pieces retain their original factory sheen. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new. The engine operates with whisper-quiet precision, and the drivetrain delivers a seamless, robust performance that mirrors its first day on the road. It has been maintained with an obsessive attention to detail, with every scheduled service performed ahead of time by master technicians. This sale includes the complete set of original keys, all owner's manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service documentation. Truly a 'no-excuses' example of automotive excellence.",
